    • PaymentInformation

      public PaymentInformation(String group_id, String user, float price, String item_id, List<String> users)
      Assigns values from the parameters to the class attribute variables.
      Parameters:
      group_id - the String which represents the ID of the group which was involved in the purchase.
      user - the User who made the purchase.
      price - the price of the item purchased represented as a float.
      item_id - the String which represents the ID of the item which was purchased.
      users - the list of all users involved in the purchase of the item;
